# Test Entity Terminology

In `*.test.js` files, keep Strapi and Meilisearch entities clearly distinct.

- Refer to Strapi entries as `Strapi entries`.
- Refer to Meilisearch entries as `indexed documents` or `Meilisearch indexed documents`.
- Do not use `entry` to refer to a Meilisearch document.

## Example

```js
// Good
const strapiEntry = await createStrapiEntry();
const indexedDocument = await fetchIndexedDocument();

// Avoid
const meilisearchEntry = await fetchIndexedDocument();
```
